# Nora CRM Agent Rule

Before making changes, read:

- `AGENTS.md`
- `docs/nora/00-project-context.md`
- `docs/nora/01-domain-model.md`
- `docs/nora/02-design-system.md`
- `docs/nora/03-data-model-guardrails.md`
- `docs/nora/04-routing-i18n.md`
- `docs/nora/06-decision-log.md`

Never blindly rename internal resources (`contacts`, `companies`, `deals`, `tasks`, `tags`). Use visible German labels and routes instead.

Do not edit `dist/` directly.

Do not create Supabase migrations or DB changes without an explicit documented decision.

Run `npm run typecheck` and `npm run build` after meaningful changes.
